{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-markdown-remark-frontmatter-slug-tsx","path":"/533/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Android だと何も設定をしなくても TextInput にフォーカスをしたらキーボードが表示されて、キーボード分せり上がって、入力ボックスが見えるけれど、iOS だと隠れてしまう。そのために KeyboardAvoidingView でラップする必要がある。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>KeyboardAvoidingView</span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token value css language-css\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span></span></span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">flex:</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">1</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">}}</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">behavior</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>padding<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>しかしこれでは不十分。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 503px; \n                margin-inline: 0;\n              \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5fd9edc6884d0ab861daec40ba0225c0/a4078/image-10.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 182.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image\"\n        title=\"image\"\n        src=\"/static/5fd9edc6884d0ab861daec40ba0225c0/a4078/image-10.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5fd9edc6884d0ab861daec40ba0225c0/8a4e8/image-10.png 150w,\n/static/5fd9edc6884d0ab861daec40ba0225c0/5a46d/image-10.png 300w,\n/static/5fd9edc6884d0ab861daec40ba0225c0/a4078/image-10.png 503w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 503px) 100vw, 503px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>何も設定していない状態</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 495px; \n                margin-inline: 0;\n              \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2a795469d14dfc5e88f9227423f34313/a4d88/image-9.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 188.66666666666669%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image\"\n        title=\"image\"\n        src=\"/static/2a795469d14dfc5e88f9227423f34313/a4d88/image-9.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2a795469d14dfc5e88f9227423f34313/8a4e8/image-9.png 150w,\n/static/2a795469d14dfc5e88f9227423f34313/5a46d/image-9.png 300w,\n/static/2a795469d14dfc5e88f9227423f34313/a4d88/image-9.png 495w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 495px) 100vw, 495px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><strong>behavior